Package: zorro
Type: Package
Title: High-Performance Xoshiro256++ Random Number Generator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("brj", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "bobjanse@gmail.com")
Description: High-performance random number generation using the xoshiro256++
    algorithm with automatic SIMD dispatch (AVX-512, AVX2, portable). Provides
    uniform, normal, exponential, and Bernoulli distributions via vectorized
    batch fill operations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
NeedsCompilation: yes
